WEBVTT

00:03.279 --> 00:06.324
HOMICIDAL HAM

00:06.490 --> 00:09.952
- Hiya, Sam.
- Hey, Carla.

00:10.119 --> 00:14.665
- Did you just get pregnant?
- No. I could, but this is just stuffing.

00:14.832 --> 00:18.294
- Why?
- I'm a little short and my rent is due.

00:18.461 --> 00:21.088
And pregnant women get better tips.

00:23.132 --> 00:27.303
It's dishonest, Sam.
You should tell her to get rid of it.

00:27.470 --> 00:29.847
I can't do that. She's Catholic.

00:33.893 --> 00:36.771
Watch it. I'm in a family way here.

